ppy/osu-wiki.summary: Recent activities involve updates to the `MWC 7K 2025` team listing and rules, including adjustments to Round of 24-related rules, adding initial team listings for eligible countries, and creating a news post for the 3 Digit World Cup 2025 registrations. These updates demonstrate a focus on maintaining accurate and up-to-date information on the osu-wiki, reflecting ongoing efforts to support the osu! community's events and activities.

ppy/osu-framework.summary: Recent activities center around enhancements and improvements to the osu-framework, including the addition of Linux ARM64 build support for FFmpeg, native macOS image loading support to significantly improve texture loading times, and cleanup of Objective-C interop code for better organization and efficiency. These contributions highlight the ongoing development and refinement of the osu-framework to enhance performance and functionality across different platforms.
